---
title: Cheesy Bean Enchiladas with DIY Guacamole
description: Dinner tonight is quick and easy! Delicious spiced beans are cooked with tomatoes and used as a perfect filling for these enchiladas. Don't forget about the gooey melted cheese and cooling DIY guacamole!
